### Welcome to LiveChat's documentation page.

* This plugin requires [Vault](http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/vault/).
* If you want to see color tags over player heads you need to install [TagAPI](http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/tag/).

_More information coming soon._
